liYa Alqamara","text_ar":"اِسْتَرْعَيْتُ مَالِىَ القَمَرَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I left my cattle to pasture without a pastor to take care of them in the night:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and [in like manner,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AstrEythu Al$~amosa","text_ar":"استرعيتهُ الشَّمْسَ"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in the day."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qmr","text_ar":"قمر"},{"kind":"text","text":".) ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AisotaroEayotuhu Al$~aYo'a","text_ar":"اِسْتَرْعَيْتُهُ الشَّىْءَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K *)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I asked him,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"desired him, to keep"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"guard,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"be mindful of"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"regardful of, the thing."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, * TA.) Hence the prov.,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mani A@sotaroEaY Al*~iy^oba faqado Zalama","text_ar":"مَنِ ا@سْتَرْعَى الذِّيْبَ فَقَدْ ظَلَمَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He who asks,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"desires, the wolf to keep guard does wrong"},{"kind":"text","text":"]; (S, TA;) i. e. he who trusts in one who is treacherous puts trust in a wrong place. (TA.) [And hence also,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AisotaroEaY AlA^asomaAEa lixuTobatihi","text_ar":"اِسْتَرْعَى الاَسْمَاعَ لِخُطْبَتِهِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He asked,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"desired, the ears"},{"kind":"text","text":"[meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the hearers"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"to mind his discourse,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"oration."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Har p. 361.)"}],"source_refs":[]}]},"classical_definitions":null}